headline: Texas Pacific Land: Future Data Center Play Through Cheap Oil, Water, And Land To Watch
summary: Texas Pacific Land is a top Permian Basin landowner, but its high valuation, low yield, and risks make it less compelling. Find out why TPL stock is a hold.
